      "index": "6",
      "number": "3",
      "title": "Stage 3: Small House",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Stage_3:_Small_House\">Stage 3: Small House</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<figure class=\"thumb  show-info-icon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\" style=\"width: 250px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/elderscrolls/images/5/5c/Hearthfireconstruction3.png/revision/latest?cb=20120828154008\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"The early stages of construction in the marshes of Hjaalmarch.\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/elderscrolls/images/5/5c/Hearthfireconstruction3.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/250?cb=20120828154008\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"250\" height=\"139\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"Hearthfireconstruction3.png\" data-image-key=\"Hearthfireconstruction3.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Hearthfireconstruction3.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">The early stages of construction in the marshes of Hjaalmarch.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<dl><dd><span><i>Main article: <a href=\"/wiki/Small_House\" title=\"Small House\">Small House</a></i></span></dd></dl>\n<p>Activating the drafting table will allow the first basic layout to begin construction. Choosing a \"Small House Layout\" will mark a rectangular plot on the land where the house will be built.\n</p><p>Next, move over to the carpenter's workbench where the foundations and supports must be laid. The required materials include quarried stone, clay and sawn logs. Once all the required items are in one's inventory, the sections of the small house can be built.\n</p><p>The small house consists of seven components that are spilt into five stages of construction:\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=\"100%\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Stage\n</th>\n<th>Section\n</th>\n<th>Sawn Log\n</th>\n<th>Quarried Stone\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Nails\" title=\"Nails\">Nails</a>\n</th>\n<th>Clay\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Iron_Fittings\" title=\"Iron Fittings\">Iron Fittings</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Lock_(Hearthfire)\" title=\"Lock (Hearthfire)\">Lock</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Hinge\" title=\"Hinge\">Hinge</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Stage 1\n</th>\n<td>House, Foundation\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>\n</th>\n<td>House, Wall Framing\n</td>\n<td>6\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Stage 2\n</th>\n<td>House, Walls\n</td>\n<td>2\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>8\n</td>\n<td>4\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Stage 3\n</th>\n<td>House, Floor\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>4\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>\n</th>\n<td>House, Roof Framing\n</td>\n<td>6\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Stage 4\n</th>\n<td>House, Roof\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Stage 5\n</th>\n<td>House, Door\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>2\n</td>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Total\n</th>\n<td>-\n</td>\n<td>17\n</td>\n<td>14\n</td>\n<td>30\n</td>\n<td>4\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>2\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260717014304\nCache expiry: 1209600\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.016 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 6/1000000\